WEBVTT

00:01:35.830 --> 00:01:38.259
[Too Young To Love]

00:01:38.509 --> 00:01:41.289
[Episode 16]

00:01:55.509 --> 00:01:56.310
What's wrong?

00:01:58.070 --> 00:02:01.260
Whose girlfriend is this beautiful lady?

00:02:01.490 --> 00:02:02.090
Oh, right.

00:02:02.290 --> 00:02:02.730
Mine.

00:02:04.530 --> 00:02:05.930
Where is your e-scooter?

00:02:06.190 --> 00:02:08.120
It's so bright and sunny today—

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:09.389
perfect for a nice stroll

00:02:09.389 --> 00:02:10.710
and a little shopping.

00:02:10.729 --> 00:02:12.240
What do you say, my lady?

00:02:12.270 --> 00:02:13.200
Sure.

00:02:13.510 --> 00:02:14.230
Then...

00:02:14.820 --> 00:02:15.350
Let's go.

00:02:16.460 --> 00:02:17.090
Let's go.

00:02:22.540 --> 00:02:24.000
The sun is so strong today.

00:02:24.390 --> 00:02:26.520
What if my girlfriend gets sunburned?

00:02:26.660 --> 00:02:27.340
Lan,

00:02:27.340 --> 00:02:30.030
do you want to go somewhere else
for our date?

00:02:30.030 --> 00:02:31.100
Let's go to the musical instrument store.

00:02:31.100 --> 00:02:32.829
The musical instrument store?

00:02:33.500 --> 00:02:34.310
You

00:02:34.620 --> 00:02:35.060
don't

00:02:35.230 --> 00:02:37.829
still have feelings for Shan, do you?

00:02:37.850 --> 00:02:39.380
What are you talking about?

00:02:40.380 --> 00:02:41.060
I...

00:02:41.750 --> 00:02:42.940
invited Mengmeng.

00:02:46.590 --> 00:02:48.510
It's our first date today,

00:02:48.620 --> 00:02:50.260
and you invited Mengmeng?

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:51.780
Mengmeng just went through a breakup.

00:02:51.780 --> 00:02:53.640
She needs some company right now.

00:02:53.640 --> 00:02:54.820
Besides, she won't come until evening.

00:02:54.820 --> 00:02:56.500
It won't affect our date.

00:02:57.400 --> 00:02:59.840
I'm not sure I want her to come.

00:02:59.870 --> 00:03:00.990
Please.

00:03:01.010 --> 00:03:02.610
You're the absolute best

00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:04.700
boyfriend in the entire world, okay?

00:03:05.100 --> 00:03:06.150
Fine, I guess...

00:03:07.660 --> 00:03:08.340
Are you alright?

00:03:08.340 --> 00:03:09.500
I'm fine.

00:03:11.940 --> 00:03:12.500
Wait.

00:03:13.030 --> 00:03:14.360
Your shoelace is loose.

00:03:18.100 --> 00:03:19.470
What if you trip and fall later?

00:03:19.470 --> 00:03:21.910
-I won't.
-Look carefully when you walk.

00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:23.040
Check these things.

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:25.870
People are coming. Get up.

00:03:25.870 --> 00:03:26.750
Not done tying yet.

00:03:26.750 --> 00:03:27.470
Xiaole!

00:03:28.060 --> 00:03:29.170
-Uncle Li, hello.
-What kind of surprise

00:03:29.170 --> 00:03:30.340
-have you got for Yi Lan this time?
-Uncle Wang, hello.

00:03:30.340 --> 00:03:31.870
No, her shoelace was untied.
I was tying it.

00:03:31.870 --> 00:03:34.510
Lan, don't let Xiaole
sweep you off your feet.

00:03:34.660 --> 00:03:36.190
Your dad is really worried.

00:03:36.950 --> 00:03:38.210
I know, Uncle.

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:41.040
Let's go. Let's go.

00:03:43.030 --> 00:03:44.060
Xiaole, going on a date?

00:03:44.060 --> 00:03:44.780
Hello, Aunties.

00:03:44.780 --> 00:03:45.340
Yeah.

00:03:46.100 --> 00:03:47.750
Look, what a lovely couple.

00:03:48.340 --> 00:03:49.540
Yeah. Have a nice day.

00:03:49.750 --> 00:03:50.310
Okay.

00:03:50.310 --> 00:03:51.060
Bye.

00:03:53.190 --> 00:03:55.470
Everyone in the neighborhood knows us.

00:03:55.470 --> 00:03:57.060
Can we keep a low profile?

00:03:57.100 --> 00:03:58.470
So what?

00:03:58.500 --> 00:04:00.060
I'm not embarrassed.

00:04:00.060 --> 00:04:01.340
You're my girlfriend.

00:04:01.660 --> 00:04:03.260
I'm not embarrassed either.

00:04:03.660 --> 00:04:05.780
But I'm just shy.

00:04:05.780 --> 00:04:06.540
Shy?

00:04:06.820 --> 00:04:08.820
-Let's go!
-Yi Lan is my girlfriend!

00:04:08.820 --> 00:04:09.540
Let's go!

00:04:11.270 --> 00:04:12.430
Sir, miss,

00:04:13.340 --> 00:04:14.940
your afternoon tea is ready.

00:04:15.060 --> 00:04:16.029
Thanks, Shan.

00:04:16.029 --> 00:04:16.540
Please enjoy.

00:04:16.540 --> 00:04:18.200
Thanks for the service, Shan.

00:04:33.090 --> 00:04:34.930
Why do you keep staring at me?

00:04:35.420 --> 00:04:36.420
Mm...

00:04:37.659 --> 00:04:38.420
Because...

00:04:38.740 --> 00:04:39.659
you're pretty.

00:04:41.420 --> 00:04:42.740
You're good-looking too.

00:04:42.740 --> 00:04:43.300
Oh?

00:04:45.090 --> 00:04:46.070
Which part?

00:04:47.070 --> 00:04:48.220
Hmm...

00:04:48.659 --> 00:04:49.630
Your eyes...

00:04:50.300 --> 00:04:51.360
are big and bright.

00:04:52.210 --> 00:04:55.930
Your nose looks like
it's straight out of a comic.

00:04:55.960 --> 00:04:57.520
And your lips...

00:04:57.540 --> 00:04:59.980
your lips look nice too.

00:05:04.740 --> 00:05:05.940
Don't say "oh" again.

00:05:08.100 --> 00:05:08.830
Then tell me.

00:05:10.510 --> 00:05:12.370
Who's better looking, me or Shan?

00:05:12.930 --> 00:05:16.130
Of course, my boyfriend looks the best.

00:05:16.180 --> 00:05:18.740
The best-looking in the whole wide world!

00:05:20.420 --> 00:05:21.620
Keep it down, you two!

00:05:21.740 --> 00:05:22.660
I can hear everything.

00:05:22.660 --> 00:05:23.340
Shh.

00:05:26.830 --> 00:05:29.170
Let's have some cake.

00:05:32.950 --> 00:05:33.540
Is it good?

00:05:33.540 --> 00:05:33.950
Yeah.

00:05:34.420 --> 00:05:35.020
It's good.

00:05:35.740 --> 00:05:36.220
I...

00:05:36.300 --> 00:05:37.230
I want a bite too.

00:05:38.180 --> 00:05:39.180
Here, have a bite.

00:05:42.470 --> 00:05:45.100
Big news! Big news!

00:05:51.510 --> 00:05:52.220
Chen Fan...

00:05:52.830 --> 00:05:54.159
Chen Fan got cheated on.

00:05:55.830 --> 00:05:56.540
I heard Ning

00:05:56.540 --> 00:05:58.390
got together with a violinist.

00:05:59.980 --> 00:06:01.780
How do you know that?

00:06:05.950 --> 00:06:07.410
Someone posted this video

00:06:07.510 --> 00:06:08.660
online.

00:06:08.780 --> 00:06:10.340
I called Chen Fan the other day.

00:06:10.340 --> 00:06:11.180
He was wasted

00:06:11.270 --> 00:06:13.270
and said Ning had broken up with him.

00:06:13.300 --> 00:06:14.830
Isn't that obvious enough?

00:06:15.180 --> 00:06:15.660
Impossible.

00:06:15.660 --> 00:06:17.390
Ning isn't that kind of person.

00:06:20.540 --> 00:06:23.000
You two don't actually believe that,
do you?

00:06:28.540 --> 00:06:29.540
He didn't answer.

00:06:29.780 --> 00:06:31.440
I can't reach Chen Fan either.

00:06:31.740 --> 00:06:32.600
He probably...

00:06:32.740 --> 00:06:34.860
broke down
and didn't want us to laugh at him.

00:06:34.860 --> 00:06:36.100
I told you,

00:06:36.220 --> 00:06:37.540
simps always end up

00:06:37.630 --> 00:06:38.830
with nothing.

00:06:41.540 --> 00:06:43.140
Can either of you reach Ning?

00:06:43.710 --> 00:06:45.300
I haven't been in touch
with her lately either.

00:06:45.300 --> 00:06:46.830
Maybe she's working part-time—

00:06:46.830 --> 00:06:47.630
she's so busy.

00:06:48.460 --> 00:06:48.940
Lan.

00:06:49.659 --> 00:06:50.420
Tong,

00:06:50.590 --> 00:06:50.690
you finally remembered me.

00:06:50.690 --> 00:06:51.720
[Chen Fan]

00:06:52.030 --> 00:06:53.030
He replied to you.

00:06:53.540 --> 00:06:54.180
Yeah.

00:06:54.180 --> 00:06:55.100
Well...

00:06:55.980 --> 00:06:57.740
I'll go find him then.

00:06:58.180 --> 00:06:58.740
Go...

00:06:59.180 --> 00:07:00.300
Go ahead.

00:07:00.630 --> 00:07:01.740
Sorry.

00:07:02.910 --> 00:07:03.660
Okay, I'm going then.

00:07:03.660 --> 00:07:03.980
Mm.

00:07:04.660 --> 00:07:05.180
Bye.

00:07:11.090 --> 00:07:11.690
Mengmeng,

00:07:11.980 --> 00:07:12.940
how have you been lately?

00:07:12.940 --> 00:07:14.140
Did you and your ex...

00:07:19.150 --> 00:07:20.750
I tried to get back together,

00:07:21.300 --> 00:07:23.300
but he already has a new girlfriend.

00:07:48.659 --> 00:07:49.590
Catch and shoot!

00:08:03.390 --> 00:08:04.790
Let's stop. Take a break.

00:08:05.980 --> 00:08:07.180
I'll go wash my hands.

00:08:08.220 --> 00:08:12.150
[Wash Basin]

00:08:12.150 --> 00:08:12.950
Come on.

00:08:19.710 --> 00:08:20.830
Don't mess with me.

00:08:39.260 --> 00:08:40.450
Come on.

00:08:49.900 --> 00:08:50.620
Have some?

00:08:56.180 --> 00:08:56.910
Tell me,

00:08:57.490 --> 00:08:59.020
what happened with you two?

00:09:03.270 --> 00:09:04.180
Tell me...

00:09:05.580 --> 00:09:07.640
did I really not understand her well?

00:09:09.890 --> 00:09:10.800
We broke up.

00:09:13.190 --> 00:09:14.190
She initiated it?

00:09:20.110 --> 00:09:21.910
Then what are you planning to do?

00:09:22.780 --> 00:09:24.180
My head is all over the place right now.

00:09:24.180 --> 00:09:25.660
I don't know what to do.

00:09:27.180 --> 00:09:29.700
It's just a breakup.
Is it worth all this drama?

00:09:29.700 --> 00:09:30.940
You're acting so pathetic.

00:09:30.940 --> 00:09:32.600
Don't make me look down on you.

00:09:35.300 --> 00:09:36.870
Why is dating so hard?

00:09:37.220 --> 00:09:37.910
Do you think

00:09:38.060 --> 00:09:39.820
she ever liked me at all?

00:09:42.660 --> 00:09:44.660
Whether she ever truly liked you...

00:09:45.270 --> 00:09:47.350
only you know that deep down.

00:09:48.030 --> 00:09:49.270
But I think

00:09:49.460 --> 00:09:51.390
she has always been someone who...

00:09:52.060 --> 00:09:53.270
admires strength.

00:09:54.660 --> 00:09:56.320
Her getting together with you

00:09:56.540 --> 00:09:59.060
in the first place might have just been
a pure coincidence.

00:09:59.060 --> 00:10:00.420
I really am pathetic.

00:10:01.420 --> 00:10:03.680
She even looked down on me over a breakup.

00:10:07.510 --> 00:10:08.350
Don't tell Mengmeng

00:10:08.350 --> 00:10:09.750
that you and I are dating.

00:10:10.150 --> 00:10:12.460
I have to help Mengmeng heal
before school starts,

00:10:12.460 --> 00:10:13.870
so let's not date for now.

00:10:15.110 --> 00:10:16.310
Get up, get up, get up.

00:10:16.540 --> 00:10:17.180
Get up.

00:10:20.780 --> 00:10:22.270
Do you know

00:10:22.270 --> 00:10:24.470
what's most important to you right now?

00:10:26.460 --> 00:10:28.260
It's to make yourself stronger.

00:10:31.420 --> 00:10:32.510
How can I do that?

00:10:35.150 --> 00:10:36.990
Don't you have a talent for composition?

00:10:36.990 --> 00:10:38.320
Use your musical talent

00:10:38.390 --> 00:10:39.250
to win her back.

00:10:41.780 --> 00:10:42.820
It's that...

00:10:45.630 --> 00:10:46.490
you need space.

00:10:47.420 --> 00:10:48.460
You need to grow.

00:10:49.270 --> 00:10:50.400
You need restraint.

00:10:51.420 --> 00:10:53.680
Do you understand what restraint means?

00:10:54.940 --> 00:10:56.300
Think about it.

00:10:59.580 --> 00:11:01.940
Just as trees need pruning
to grow straight,

00:11:01.940 --> 00:11:03.940
people need discipline to shape up.

00:11:06.660 --> 00:11:07.180
Uncle!

00:11:08.060 --> 00:11:09.660
Xiaole, you're back!

00:11:10.030 --> 00:11:10.540
Xuan.

00:11:10.940 --> 00:11:12.030
Where is Lan?

00:11:12.030 --> 00:11:13.390
We should be heading to school now.

00:11:13.390 --> 00:11:14.300
She's probably still sleeping.

00:11:14.300 --> 00:11:15.630
Not sure if she's up yet.

00:11:16.990 --> 00:11:17.750
Mm.

00:11:19.300 --> 00:11:20.360
I'll go wake her up.

00:11:20.540 --> 00:11:21.030
Okay.

00:12:12.780 --> 00:12:14.220
♪ I can see you once I open my eyes ♪

00:12:14.660 --> 00:12:16.300
♪ Silly me, can't help but gaze at you ♪

00:12:16.300 --> 00:12:16.790
You're awake.

00:12:16.790 --> 00:12:18.660
♪ Your love is like a pink cloud ♪

00:12:18.660 --> 00:12:19.580
Mm?

00:12:20.680 --> 00:12:21.700
♪ Whenever you come near ♪

00:12:21.700 --> 00:12:22.390
Rise and shine.

00:12:22.390 --> 00:12:23.390
♪ I lose myself in you ♪

00:12:23.390 --> 00:12:25.370
Why are you still in bed, sleepyhead?

00:12:25.370 --> 00:12:25.910
♪ The corners of my mouth turn up
simply at the thought of you ♪

00:12:25.910 --> 00:12:27.180
Why are you here?

00:12:29.150 --> 00:12:29.300
♪ My IQ goes to zero ♪

00:12:29.300 --> 00:12:30.300
You didn't forget

00:12:30.460 --> 00:12:31.010
school starts today, did you?

00:12:31.010 --> 00:12:32.640
♪ Calories are my only cure ♪

00:12:33.090 --> 00:12:33.420
♪ I want a cup of boba tea with sugar ♪

00:12:33.420 --> 00:12:34.780
I didn't forget.

00:12:35.420 --> 00:12:37.220
I was up really late last night
practicing the cello.

00:12:37.220 --> 00:12:38.790
♪ With you around ♪

00:12:38.920 --> 00:12:39.780
♪ I feel like an untethered wild horse ♪

00:12:39.780 --> 00:12:41.760
Really late, huh?

00:12:41.760 --> 00:12:42.850
♪ Love is the reason for gaining weight ♪

00:12:42.850 --> 00:12:45.170
Have you been thinking about me
every day lately?

00:12:45.170 --> 00:12:48.190
♪ Boba tea with sugar means I like you ♪

00:12:48.650 --> 00:12:50.040
♪ Warm palms ♪

00:12:50.460 --> 00:12:50.650
Yes.

00:12:50.650 --> 00:12:52.230
♪ The pleasant smell of love ♪

00:12:52.530 --> 00:12:53.060
♪ I sync my playlist with yours
in secret ♪

00:12:53.060 --> 00:12:53.920
What about you?

00:12:54.790 --> 00:12:55.710
♪ Let our hearts beat in sync ♪

00:12:55.810 --> 00:12:56.530
♪ Let us breathe in sync ♪

00:12:56.530 --> 00:12:57.300
Of course.

00:12:57.750 --> 00:12:58.060
♪ I absolutely, totally,
and utterly adore you ♪

00:12:58.060 --> 00:13:00.060
I've been thinking about you

00:13:00.080 --> 00:13:01.530
so, so, so much.

00:13:01.530 --> 00:13:02.450
♪ Boba tea with sugar ♪

00:13:02.870 --> 00:13:04.430
♪ My dream for each new day ♪

00:13:04.870 --> 00:13:06.270
♪ Is to hold you ♪

00:13:06.270 --> 00:13:06.870
You go out first.

00:13:06.870 --> 00:13:07.540
♪ And have fun, hee-hee ♪

00:13:07.540 --> 00:13:08.910
I'll get up in a bit.

00:13:08.910 --> 00:13:08.960
No.

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:10.190
♪ Without doubt ♪

00:13:10.240 --> 00:13:10.660
♪ The boba ♪

00:13:10.660 --> 00:13:11.020
I want to stay a little longer.

00:13:11.020 --> 00:13:12.190
♪ And pudding in my tea ♪

00:13:12.250 --> 00:13:13.540
♪ Are all yours ♪

00:13:13.950 --> 00:13:15.660
♪ You are everything I want ♪

00:13:15.660 --> 00:13:16.780
Just go out first.

00:13:16.780 --> 00:13:18.030
No.

00:13:34.130 --> 00:13:35.630
♪ I can see you once I open my eyes ♪

00:13:36.010 --> 00:13:37.740
♪ Silly me, can't help but gaze at you ♪

00:13:38.240 --> 00:13:41.080
♪ Your love is like a pink cloud ♪

00:13:41.660 --> 00:13:42.060
I haven't brushed my teeth yet.

00:13:42.060 --> 00:13:43.770
♪ Whenever you come near ♪

00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:44.540
♪ I lose myself in you ♪

00:13:44.540 --> 00:13:45.540
That's fine.

00:13:46.820 --> 00:13:47.540
♪ The corners of my mouth turn up
simply at the thought of you ♪

00:13:47.540 --> 00:13:48.390
To me,

00:13:48.820 --> 00:13:50.550
everything about you is sweet.

00:13:50.590 --> 00:13:52.170
♪ My IQ goes to zero ♪

00:13:52.460 --> 00:13:54.080
♪ Calories are my only cure ♪

00:13:54.540 --> 00:13:56.460
♪ I want a cup of boba tea with sugar ♪

00:13:56.460 --> 00:13:58.790
Why aren't you coming down for breakfast?

00:13:58.910 --> 00:13:59.460
Dad!

00:14:00.660 --> 00:14:01.540
X-Xiaole, you...

00:14:01.540 --> 00:14:02.200
Uncle Dong,

00:14:02.420 --> 00:14:02.820
I'm...

00:14:02.940 --> 00:14:03.910
doing sit-ups.

00:14:05.060 --> 00:14:06.390
Morning exercise, huh.

00:14:06.390 --> 00:14:07.390
Come down and eat.

00:14:10.940 --> 00:14:12.580
You okay?

00:14:15.660 --> 00:14:16.590
I'm heading out!

00:14:20.180 --> 00:14:21.710
What's wrong? You alright?

00:14:23.270 --> 00:14:24.670
Did you get hurt just now?

00:14:25.270 --> 00:14:27.030
My back hurts a bit.
Probably from the fall earlier.

00:14:27.030 --> 00:14:27.540
Lan!

00:14:28.460 --> 00:14:30.060
Scatterbrain, you forgot your bag!

00:14:30.060 --> 00:14:31.420
Oh, right. I forgot! I forgot.

00:14:31.420 --> 00:14:32.550
Let me drive you two.

00:14:32.940 --> 00:14:34.300
No need, Dad. We can go by ourselves.

00:14:34.300 --> 00:14:35.940
It's fine. I'm heading that way anyway.

00:14:35.940 --> 00:14:36.300
Dad!

00:14:36.540 --> 00:14:39.060
Can't you give me
some respect and freedom?

00:14:39.940 --> 00:14:40.580
Fine.

00:14:41.990 --> 00:14:43.050
Come on, come here.

00:14:43.540 --> 00:14:44.600
I'm telling you...

00:14:46.270 --> 00:14:47.460
Listen to me.

00:14:48.060 --> 00:14:50.390
You can't spend the night alone together.

00:14:50.460 --> 00:14:51.820
I-I know, I know.

00:14:52.660 --> 00:14:53.390
Don't worry.

00:14:53.390 --> 00:14:53.910
Mm.

00:14:56.700 --> 00:14:57.300
And you,

00:14:58.060 --> 00:14:59.180
be careful, okay?

00:15:00.060 --> 00:15:01.300
Oh, okay, Uncle Dong.

00:15:10.540 --> 00:15:11.250
How about

00:15:11.420 --> 00:15:13.390
we take a taxi instead?

00:15:15.390 --> 00:15:16.630
That works.

00:15:16.780 --> 00:15:17.580
But let's

00:15:17.700 --> 00:15:21.110
watch a movie before going to school.

00:15:21.820 --> 00:15:22.350
No,

00:15:22.580 --> 00:15:23.970
I have to practice the cello today.

00:15:23.970 --> 00:15:25.580
Professor Ye's audition is next week.

00:15:25.580 --> 00:15:27.380
I need to drill my fundamentals.

00:15:27.910 --> 00:15:29.940
I've already waited the whole summer.

00:15:29.940 --> 00:15:31.780
Are you telling me
I have to wait another week?

00:15:31.780 --> 00:15:34.860
Your boyfriend is so pitiful...

00:15:34.880 --> 00:15:36.180
The opening week is packed with classes.

00:15:36.180 --> 00:15:37.540
Focus on your studies first.

00:15:37.540 --> 00:15:39.340
I'll be free after the audition.

00:15:40.700 --> 00:15:41.270
Fine.

00:15:41.780 --> 00:15:43.420
But first...

00:15:43.820 --> 00:15:44.660
give me a kiss.

00:15:46.820 --> 00:15:48.220
You two haven't left yet?

00:15:48.520 --> 00:15:49.660
Uncle, we're just about to go.

00:15:49.660 --> 00:15:50.590
Yeah, right now.

00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:52.500
That brat.

00:15:58.390 --> 00:15:59.940
Excuse me, I was here first.

00:16:01.150 --> 00:16:01.780
Yi Lan!

00:16:03.060 --> 00:16:03.520
It's me.

00:16:03.820 --> 00:16:06.540
I asked you to deliver a letter
to Xiaole for me before.

00:16:06.540 --> 00:16:07.180
You're Chen Zhihan,

00:16:07.180 --> 00:16:07.910
from Class 1?

00:16:07.910 --> 00:16:08.710
Right, right!

00:16:09.940 --> 00:16:10.700
Um...

00:16:10.830 --> 00:16:12.950
I don't have Xiaole's contact info yet.

00:16:12.950 --> 00:16:14.550
Can you give me his WeChat ID?

00:16:15.470 --> 00:16:17.530
I'll let you take this practice room!

00:16:18.180 --> 00:16:19.830
Actually...

00:16:19.910 --> 00:16:21.310
Please, please, please.

00:16:21.660 --> 00:16:22.590
I'm begging you.

00:16:24.700 --> 00:16:25.960
I'll snap a photo of it.

00:16:31.820 --> 00:16:32.940
Done. Thanks.

00:16:33.460 --> 00:16:34.150
Enjoy.

00:16:38.420 --> 00:16:39.300
Lan?

00:16:40.300 --> 00:16:41.060
Ning.

00:16:41.460 --> 00:16:43.460
Why are you standing here
instead of going in to practice?

00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:44.460
Oh, it's nothing.

00:16:44.910 --> 00:16:46.700
Let's go to class together later.

00:16:46.700 --> 00:16:47.820
I've been a bit busy lately.

00:16:47.820 --> 00:16:48.820
I have a last-minute performance.

00:16:48.820 --> 00:16:49.580
You go ahead.

00:16:50.540 --> 00:16:51.180
Okay.

00:16:51.300 --> 00:16:52.030
Mm.

00:17:15.550 --> 00:17:16.609
What are you doing?

00:17:20.910 --> 00:17:21.770
Taking photos.

00:17:22.420 --> 00:17:24.150
Can you take a look at my photos?

00:17:24.660 --> 00:17:25.220
Sure.

00:17:30.590 --> 00:17:32.660
Photos like these are meant to...

00:17:33.020 --> 00:17:34.420
tell a story.

00:17:34.810 --> 00:17:35.740
You can try this—

00:17:35.830 --> 00:17:37.430
emphasize the subject more.

00:17:37.740 --> 00:17:39.150
You're so professional!

00:17:39.500 --> 00:17:41.860
I'm actually pretty good with
social media.

00:17:41.860 --> 00:17:44.660
Want me to help promote
your photography account?

00:17:44.980 --> 00:17:47.340
No thanks, I'm just
messing around with it.

00:17:47.340 --> 00:17:50.370
Then would you consider me...
as your girlfriend?

00:17:54.460 --> 00:17:56.590
Actually, I already have a girlfriend.

00:17:56.590 --> 00:17:57.420
Sorry.

00:17:57.460 --> 00:17:58.590
I don't believe you.

00:17:59.220 --> 00:18:01.550
I've never seen you with any other girl.

00:18:05.910 --> 00:18:06.980
I spend a lot of time

00:18:06.980 --> 00:18:09.240
with my girlfriend at school, actually.

00:18:10.180 --> 00:18:13.310
You don't have to make up those excuses
just to reject me.

00:18:13.350 --> 00:18:15.480
I'm going to take some more photos now.

00:18:15.830 --> 00:18:16.980
Think about it again.

00:18:16.980 --> 00:18:17.730
I'm off.

00:18:25.500 --> 00:18:26.430
What's going on?

00:18:27.350 --> 00:18:28.480
Nothing is going on.

00:18:31.740 --> 00:18:32.710
She's not bad.

00:18:33.070 --> 00:18:34.830
Thinking of moving on to a new girl?

00:18:34.830 --> 00:18:35.910
What are you talking about?

00:18:35.910 --> 00:18:36.940
Don't talk nonsense.

00:18:36.940 --> 00:18:38.020
I'm very loyal.

00:18:40.420 --> 00:18:42.150
No one's ever seen you on a date,

00:18:42.260 --> 00:18:44.660
so who would know
you're in a relationship?

00:18:45.260 --> 00:18:46.630
Who would know you're loyal?

00:18:46.630 --> 00:18:48.230
I can't be bothered with you.

00:18:51.620 --> 00:18:53.030
[New Friends; Chen Zhihan]

00:18:53.060 --> 00:18:54.980
[Hi, Yi Lan gave me your WeChat ID.]

00:18:55.000 --> 00:18:56.200
[Hope we can be friends.]

00:18:56.500 --> 00:18:56.940
See?

00:18:57.590 --> 00:18:59.520
So many girls think you're single.

00:19:05.660 --> 00:19:06.830
I'm sorry, okay?

00:19:07.150 --> 00:19:07.910
At the time,

00:19:08.630 --> 00:19:11.110
my brain went blank,
and I just gave it to her.

00:19:13.050 --> 00:19:15.910
You're really not afraid of
others chasing me, huh?

00:19:16.980 --> 00:19:18.290
I'm actually not afraid of that.

00:19:18.290 --> 00:19:19.950
You won't like her anyway.

00:19:20.940 --> 00:19:22.200
Don't you only like me?

00:19:23.830 --> 00:19:24.630
Not afraid, huh?

00:19:24.630 --> 00:19:25.240
Fine.

00:19:27.110 --> 00:19:28.440
Okay, okay, I'm afraid!

00:19:28.980 --> 00:19:29.840
Afraid of what?

00:19:30.630 --> 00:19:32.490
Afraid you'll like someone else.

00:19:35.260 --> 00:19:36.060
Alright then.

00:19:37.180 --> 00:19:38.460
You haven't

00:19:38.990 --> 00:19:40.990
really gone on dates with me lately.

00:19:41.150 --> 00:19:43.280
How are you planning to make it up to me?

00:19:43.830 --> 00:19:45.080
Make it up to you...

00:19:45.740 --> 00:19:46.790
How about

00:19:47.110 --> 00:19:49.110
I treat you to lots and lots of meals?

00:19:49.660 --> 00:19:51.150
Just meals, and that's it?

00:20:02.150 --> 00:20:03.210
Isn't that enough?

00:20:06.800 --> 00:20:07.680
No.

00:20:17.720 --> 00:20:18.980
There're others here.

00:20:20.220 --> 00:20:22.500
School's over. Nobody's here.

00:20:32.370 --> 00:20:33.170
Forget it.

00:20:54.480 --> 00:20:56.120
♪ All the stars surround you ♪

00:20:56.140 --> 00:20:57.810
♪ The moon smiles at you ♪

00:20:57.840 --> 00:21:00.980
♪ I give you all the good things
in the world ♪

00:21:01.450 --> 00:21:02.950
♪ And the light in your eyes ♪

00:21:03.060 --> 00:21:05.050
♪ Shines like diamonds ♪

00:21:05.400 --> 00:21:08.110
♪ Drawing an exclamation mark
in my world ♪

00:21:08.160 --> 00:21:09.680
♪ The evening breeze embraces you ♪

00:21:09.700 --> 00:21:11.550
♪ And I run towards you ♪

00:21:11.610 --> 00:21:14.940
♪ I hear our passionate heartbeats ♪

00:21:15.140 --> 00:21:16.710
♪ We borrow a dream ♪

00:21:16.740 --> 00:21:18.770
♪ To build a castle ♪

00:21:19.000 --> 00:21:21.470
♪ Every star is a romantic symbol ♪

00:21:21.580 --> 00:21:23.870
♪ Let me find you ♪

00:21:36.280 --> 00:21:39.090
♪ Even mountains and seas
can't separate us ♪

00:21:39.820 --> 00:21:42.870
♪ I wish I could turn into a bird
to explore the world for you ♪

00:21:43.270 --> 00:21:44.820
♪ The vast, boundless Milky Way ♪

00:21:44.840 --> 00:21:46.570
♪ Sings its tender serenade ♪

00:21:46.660 --> 00:21:48.910
♪ I can't live a second without you ♪

00:21:50.210 --> 00:21:53.480
♪ Looking forward
to the next beautiful dream ♪

00:21:53.550 --> 00:21:54.930
♪ I just want to be with you ♪

00:21:55.160 --> 00:21:58.080
♪ To see the most romantic starry sky
together ♪

00:21:58.510 --> 00:22:02.530
♪ The evening breeze tells
heartfelt emotions ♪

00:22:03.440 --> 00:22:05.080
♪ All the stars surround you ♪

00:22:05.100 --> 00:22:05.180
♪ The moon smiles at you ♪

00:22:05.180 --> 00:22:06.020
Today, I...

00:22:06.800 --> 00:22:09.940
♪ I give you all the good things
in the world ♪

00:22:10.170 --> 00:22:11.970
♪ And the light in your eyes ♪

00:22:11.990 --> 00:22:13.980
♪ Shines like diamonds ♪

00:22:14.360 --> 00:22:14.880
♪ Drawing an exclamation mark
in my world ♪

00:22:14.880 --> 00:22:15.680
Thank you.

00:22:17.250 --> 00:22:18.770
♪ The evening breeze embraces you ♪

00:22:18.790 --> 00:22:20.540
♪ And I run towards you ♪

00:22:20.600 --> 00:22:23.890
♪ I hear our passionate heartbeats ♪

00:22:24.110 --> 00:22:27.720
♪ To build a castle ♪

00:22:28.140 --> 00:22:30.470
♪ Every star is a romantic symbol ♪

00:22:30.520 --> 00:22:31.740
♪ Let me find you ♪

00:22:31.740 --> 00:22:32.740
Xiaole!

00:22:34.700 --> 00:22:36.190
I've mastered the photography technique

00:22:36.190 --> 00:22:37.850
you taught me last time. Look.

00:22:40.740 --> 00:22:42.000
You've improved a lot.

00:22:42.020 --> 00:22:44.220
Next, you can try shooting
some night scenes,

00:22:44.220 --> 00:22:45.390
work more with Bulb mode,

00:22:45.390 --> 00:22:46.350
and take some long-exposure shots.

00:22:46.350 --> 00:22:46.740
Okay.

00:22:47.550 --> 00:22:48.070
Yi Lan?

00:22:49.310 --> 00:22:49.910
Manman.

00:22:50.700 --> 00:22:51.700
Finished practicing?

00:22:51.700 --> 00:22:52.180
Yeah.

00:22:52.460 --> 00:22:54.320
Your club has a lot of activities.

00:22:54.650 --> 00:22:55.410
Oh, right,

00:22:55.830 --> 00:22:58.390
are you coming to
the outdoor shoot this weekend?

00:22:58.390 --> 00:22:59.920
I almost forgot about that.

00:23:00.350 --> 00:23:00.870
Sure.

00:23:01.150 --> 00:23:02.420
I'll contact you then.

00:23:02.740 --> 00:23:03.110
Bye.

00:23:03.350 --> 00:23:04.020
Bye, Yi Lan.

00:23:04.390 --> 00:23:04.940
Bye.

00:23:08.390 --> 00:23:11.350
You finished practice pretty early today.

00:23:11.660 --> 00:23:13.740
Why were you just standing there quietly
by yourself?

00:23:13.740 --> 00:23:14.910
No, I just got here.

00:23:15.350 --> 00:23:15.940
Let's go.

00:23:24.660 --> 00:23:26.420
Mengmeng, can I tell you something?

00:23:26.420 --> 00:23:27.110
Go ahead.

00:23:29.940 --> 00:23:31.600
Xiaole and I are together now.

00:23:34.220 --> 00:23:34.830
Who?

00:23:35.590 --> 00:23:36.830
Tong Xiaole?

00:23:39.660 --> 00:23:40.420
I'm mad.

00:23:40.870 --> 00:23:41.910
You're mad?

00:23:42.830 --> 00:23:44.960
You didn't tell me you two were dating.

00:23:45.490 --> 00:23:47.570
You just went through a breakup
over the summer.

00:23:47.570 --> 00:23:49.830
I didn't even have the chance to tell you.

00:23:49.870 --> 00:23:51.530
Don't be mad anymore, please.

00:23:52.020 --> 00:23:52.910
I forgive you.

00:23:55.260 --> 00:23:57.150
But the way you two are acting...

00:23:58.500 --> 00:24:01.220
it doesn't look like
you're in a relationship at all.

00:24:01.220 --> 00:24:02.350
What do you mean?

00:24:03.310 --> 00:24:04.920
You're not with him—

00:24:05.260 --> 00:24:07.220
you're here chatting with me instead.

00:24:07.220 --> 00:24:07.700
Isn't that because...

00:24:07.700 --> 00:24:08.090
you

00:24:08.110 --> 00:24:09.390
rarely come to see me?

00:24:09.390 --> 00:24:10.850
I should keep you company.

00:24:11.500 --> 00:24:13.180
Besides, I'm with him every day.

00:24:13.180 --> 00:24:14.660
What is there to talk about?

00:24:14.660 --> 00:24:16.760
Isn't it because you two have
known each other for too long?

00:24:16.760 --> 00:24:18.820
Normally, when you're newly dating,

00:24:18.870 --> 00:24:20.020
you two should be

00:24:20.630 --> 00:24:21.760
all over each other,

00:24:21.940 --> 00:24:23.940
not wanting to be apart for a second.

00:24:25.860 --> 00:24:26.610
Hmm.

00:24:27.260 --> 00:24:28.720
-You have a point.
-Right?

00:24:30.700 --> 00:24:32.390
Something happened today.

00:24:34.180 --> 00:24:35.420
A girl...

00:24:35.740 --> 00:24:37.140
wanted to ask Xiaole out.

00:24:37.390 --> 00:24:37.990
Is that...

00:24:38.110 --> 00:24:38.940
okay?

00:24:41.980 --> 00:24:42.940
A girl?

00:24:43.910 --> 00:24:44.970
Asking Xiaole out?

00:24:49.510 --> 00:24:51.280
You need to be more alert.

00:24:51.630 --> 00:24:53.560
Xiaole is actually quite popular.

00:24:58.280 --> 00:25:05.740
[Where are you shooting tomorrow?
Can I come?]

00:25:05.740 --> 00:25:11.080
[Sure. See you at
the school gate tomorrow morning.]

00:25:35.380 --> 00:25:38.070
[Hailand University;
Truth, Reason, Knowledge, Action]

00:25:38.070 --> 00:25:38.660
Xiaole!

00:25:39.590 --> 00:25:40.120
Morning.

00:25:40.390 --> 00:25:40.920
Morning.

00:25:41.020 --> 00:25:42.150
Let's get on the bus.

00:25:42.170 --> 00:25:42.970
You go first.

00:25:45.420 --> 00:25:47.280
Just go. I'm waiting for someone.

00:25:47.460 --> 00:25:47.870
Go.

00:25:48.550 --> 00:25:50.080
I'll wait for you on the bus.

00:25:51.110 --> 00:25:51.630
Hello.

00:25:51.740 --> 00:25:52.420
Morning.

00:25:52.740 --> 00:25:53.800
Not getting on yet?

00:25:55.460 --> 00:25:56.390
I'm waiting for someone.

00:25:56.390 --> 00:25:57.190
What's wrong?

00:25:59.510 --> 00:26:01.830
Are you joining the photo contest
this time?

00:26:01.830 --> 00:26:03.760
Probably not, I'm not interested.

00:26:03.980 --> 00:26:05.940
There's a photography exhibition
coming up.

00:26:05.940 --> 00:26:06.660
Are you interested?

00:26:06.660 --> 00:26:07.420
Xiaole!

00:26:08.420 --> 00:26:09.150
Morning!

00:26:09.350 --> 00:26:10.210
I'm getting on the bus now.

00:26:10.210 --> 00:26:10.660
Okay.

00:26:10.740 --> 00:26:11.180
Okay.

00:26:12.260 --> 00:26:13.420
I'm a bit busy this week.

00:26:13.420 --> 00:26:14.750
I'll see about it later.

00:26:18.500 --> 00:26:19.180
Here.

00:26:21.390 --> 00:26:22.850
I'm getting on the bus now.

00:26:28.020 --> 00:26:28.350
[Hailand University;
Truth, Reason, Knowledge, Action]

00:26:28.350 --> 00:26:29.150
Xiaole...

00:26:29.390 --> 00:26:30.260
I'm here!

00:26:31.590 --> 00:26:32.420
I'm not late, am I?

00:26:32.420 --> 00:26:33.220
No.

00:26:33.460 --> 00:26:35.150
Why are you carrying your cello?

00:26:35.150 --> 00:26:36.680
Just finished practicing.

00:26:37.350 --> 00:26:37.940
Alright.

00:26:38.420 --> 00:26:39.020
Let's go.

00:26:40.020 --> 00:26:41.280
Where is Liang Manman?

00:26:45.220 --> 00:26:46.420
So many people?

00:26:48.220 --> 00:26:48.680
Manman.

00:26:49.260 --> 00:26:51.720
What's the relationship between those two?

00:26:51.940 --> 00:26:52.800
I asked around.

00:26:52.870 --> 00:26:54.130
They grew up together.

00:26:54.420 --> 00:26:56.590
I thought it was only the two of you.

00:26:56.700 --> 00:26:57.900
How is that possible?

00:27:00.390 --> 00:27:03.110
You came because you were worried about
me being alone with her, didn't you?

00:27:03.110 --> 00:27:03.660
No!

00:27:04.180 --> 00:27:04.830
Xiaole!

00:27:05.450 --> 00:27:05.940
[Hailand University;
Truth, Reason, Knowledge, Action]

00:27:05.940 --> 00:27:07.070
Get on the bus first.

00:27:07.740 --> 00:27:08.110
Okay.

00:27:08.420 --> 00:27:08.950
Let's go.

00:27:09.180 --> 00:27:10.580
There're so many people.

00:27:14.940 --> 00:27:16.460
Isn't this a junior
from the music department?

00:27:16.460 --> 00:27:16.920
Xiaole,

00:27:16.980 --> 00:27:17.830
introduce us.

00:27:18.590 --> 00:27:19.220
This is...

00:27:19.390 --> 00:27:20.050
Hello, everyone.

00:27:20.050 --> 00:27:20.830
I'm Yi Lan.

00:27:20.940 --> 00:27:23.350
-Welcome, new friend!
-Welcome, welcome!

00:27:31.090 --> 00:27:32.160
Put it here.

00:27:36.870 --> 00:27:38.020
I can hold it myself.

00:27:38.020 --> 00:27:39.150
It's safer this way.

00:27:43.350 --> 00:27:44.480
Sit with me, Xiaole.

00:27:48.390 --> 00:27:48.720
Okay.

00:27:49.180 --> 00:27:49.700
Thanks.

00:27:52.700 --> 00:27:53.350
Driver,

00:27:53.660 --> 00:27:55.220
we're all here. Let's go.

00:28:12.970 --> 00:28:13.630
Xiaole!

00:28:14.180 --> 00:28:15.240
What are you doing?

00:28:15.810 --> 00:28:18.320
Did you find any nice compositions?

00:28:18.420 --> 00:28:19.460
Yes, look.

00:28:20.270 --> 00:28:20.750
Okay.

00:28:26.690 --> 00:28:27.490
Not bad!

00:28:27.990 --> 00:28:29.180
You've gotten

00:28:29.180 --> 00:28:31.780
so much better at composition
since last time.

00:28:32.110 --> 00:28:34.040
It's all thanks to you teaching me.

00:28:34.320 --> 00:28:35.450
Do you have time now?

00:28:35.660 --> 00:28:37.080
Would you like me to show you

00:28:37.080 --> 00:28:38.410
how to run your account?

00:28:42.110 --> 00:28:43.020
Ouch!

00:28:43.020 --> 00:28:43.790
What's wrong? What's wrong?

00:28:43.790 --> 00:28:44.310
It hurts.

00:28:44.310 --> 00:28:44.660
It hurts?

00:28:44.660 --> 00:28:45.220
I sprained my ankle.

00:28:45.220 --> 00:28:45.770
It really hurts.

00:28:45.770 --> 00:28:46.180
You twisted your ankle?

00:28:46.180 --> 00:28:47.180
My hand hurts too!

00:28:47.870 --> 00:28:48.630
Let me take a look.

00:28:48.630 --> 00:28:51.090
You have to blow on it
to make the pain go away.

00:28:51.180 --> 00:28:52.150
I have to blow on it?

00:28:52.150 --> 00:28:52.700
Mm.

00:28:53.660 --> 00:28:55.220
I'll blow on it. Does it feel better?

00:28:55.220 --> 00:28:56.180
No more pain, right?

00:28:56.180 --> 00:28:57.700
Don't be mad at me anymore.

00:28:59.500 --> 00:29:00.650
I'm not mad.

00:29:00.740 --> 00:29:01.830
I was wrong.

00:29:02.220 --> 00:29:03.940
From now on, I'll always
sit next to you, okay?